settings.heading: PRODUCTS MUMMA MILLA LOVES AND RECOMMENDS

settings.text: We've collated a few of our favourites items that are beautiful, functional, wonderful quality and will see you through if your family grows over the next few years too.

settings.heading: NUAGE INTERIORS
settings.p-desc:
Our favourite rockers and armchairs from Nuage.
Nursing is a precious ritual – and while you’re nourishing your baby, you deserve an empathetically-designed chair to support you. An elegant blend of style and structure that will seamlessly flatter your home’s existing colour palette, with a grand silhouette that punctuates the room.

settings.heading: YOUHA BREAST PUMPS
settings.p-desc: The Cordless Breast Pumps by Youha are a favourite. They offer the convenience of powerful hands-free pumping with great collection capacity. Control your The INs remotely and track your breast milk by connecting with  the YOUHA app. These can easily fit into the MUMMA MILLA nursing bralettes so you can express whilst you are busy with baby, doing house chores, or at work.  Use code MM10 for 10% off breast pumps.

settings.heading: THE MAMA PHYSIO
settings.p-desc:
Stay strong, pain and leak-free during your pregnancy and rehabilitate your pelvic floor and abdominal muscles under the guidance of a Women’s Health Physio in the comfort of your own home.   Use the code MUMMAMILLA for a 20% discount off the monthly and yearly MOVE memberships.

Jess Jenkins is an Advanced Practice Physiotherapist in Pelvic Health,                                                       Clinical & Fitness Pilates Instructor                                                                                                 Ante & Postnatal Pilates Course Educator, and Mother.

settings.heading: BUTTERFLY MATERNITY PILLOW
settings.p-desc:
Made to support you and your baby form pregnancy to postpartum
The Butterfly Maternity Pillow has a distinctive wedge-shaped design which supports both your lower back and your growing bump. The body-hugging butterfly wings cradle your bump, aligning your hips and lower back and dispersing pressure evenly to ensure deep rest. Use the code MUMMAMILLA for 10% off.

settings.heading: THE DUO PACK OF SILVERETTES
settings.p-desc:
A breastfeeding lifesaver! 
Silverettes are recommended for mums to prevent cracked, sore and irritated nipple skin from breastfeeding or expressing milk, soothe and heal in between cluster feeds and to use at any stage of the mother’s lactation journey. A great option to pack into your hospital bag and they can easily be placed inside our leakproof bralettes.

settings.heading: HAAKAA LADY BUG
settings.p-desc:
A silicone milk collector that you can wear inside your MUMMA MILLA Bralettes or Cami. The Ladybug Milk Collector will  collect any let down milk that would otherwise be lost in the leakproof layers. The comfortable and discreet one-piece design attaches securely to your breast and fits on the inside of your bra to catch those precious drops of breastmilk. 
Use the code: MUMMAMILLA for 10% off.

settings.heading: BUGABOO FOX 5
settings.p-desc:
All-terrain strolls from day one
Go further than ever imagined. The Bugaboo Fox 5 is the most comfortable go-anywhere pram suitable for newborns to toddlers.​ Offering a smooth ride on all terrains, with a one-hand fold, it’s engineered for an easy start on your parenting journey.
